{"tid":1821081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(街馬)疑有跑手用水槍顏射廢柴張建宗","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T04:26:20.000Z","uid":125168,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"50a8b2da725517712ca61e654f0c536202093cd2","tid":1821081,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗出席活動時　疑被跑手用水槍噴中2020/01/12 11:27<br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】政務司司長張建宗清晨出席一個馬拉松起步禮時，懷疑被跑手用水槍噴中。張建宗事後用手抹頭及整理風褸。<br />\n<br />\n事發於早上近6時，東區走廊正舉行「香港街馬」32公里賽。張建宗在台上為跑手打氣，有經過的跑手舉高手，又喊「光復香港」口號。其間有跑手用水槍射向台上，液體濺中張建宗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/15199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F15199&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=518f45f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F15199&h=75fe6b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/15199</a>"},{"pid":"697818304ddfa2887a18e55d803ab0cf04dcc78b","tid":1821081,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23c143e3c090e46e0803cc08fbb0686cc515e0c","tid":1821081,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22fdc2255208fa338b44d3801c8874aa742395fe","tid":1821081,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"感謝手足"},{"pid":"cff01d2eef5742f043c6a8fe1004460d2fcad1b7","tid":1821081,"uid":343017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeQ7bDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai